<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>源码与技术服务选购小程序及管理系统需求文档</title>
  <style>
    @page { margin: 2.4cm 2.2cm; }
    body {
      font-family: "Microsoft YaHei", "SimSun", Arial, sans-serif;
      font-size: 10.5pt;
